NEWS - list of all major game and engine changes

New in rd-132328
* Rewrite version: rd-132328.
* Engine version 0.03.
* libgfx version: 0.02.
* Enable selector and player pick from code.
* Delete cave generation.
* Add interpolation factor in OnRender().
* Change all type definition.
* Optimize frustum CubeInside() function.
* Add support for different image channels in texture reported by stb_image.
* Fix chunk border detext intervals.
* Add Entity class.
* Some functions of Player passed to Entity.
* Invert mouse input.
* Separed Pick() function.
* Add char.png texture
* Add 100 Zombies.
* Add Character shader.

New in rd-131655 (Cave game tech)
* Recreated version: rd-131655 from https://github.com/thecodeofnotch/rd-131655
* Engine version: 0.02
* libgfx version: 0.02
* Disable selector and player pick from code.
* Change log system to spdlog bassed log system.
* Add random cave generator from code https://github.com/thecodeofnotch/rd-131655/blob/master/src/main/java/com/mojang/rubydung/level/Level.java.
* Improve mesh generation.
* Refractor core/common.h
* Improve TODO list.
* Refractor cmake files.
* Add spdlog as dependency.
* Change x,y,z convention in engine.
* The version in the game is exactly like the original versions.
* Disable C4251 warning.
* Disable C4996 warning.
* Change versioning to semver in the engine.
* Clean code.
* Improve documentation.
* Add commit check workflow to git repository.

New in rd-132211-5 - 26-08-25
* Rewrite version: rd-132211.
* Engine version 0.0.2-prealpha.
* libgfx PATCH 1 version 0.02-prealpha.
* Final version.

New in rd-132211-4 - 23-08-25:
* Rewrite version: rd-132211.
* Engine version 0.0.2-prealpha.
* libgfx PATCH 1 version 0.02-prealpha.
* libgfx is now part of main repository (lib/gfx and include/lib/gfx).
* Sandbox renamed to game
* Improved log subsystem bugs.
* Deleted mc_fmt() macro in log subsystem.
* MC_LOG_USE_RELPATH macro for use relpaths in log subsystem.
* Solved game and engine bugs.
* Changed all prefix of typedefs mc instead of rd.
* Deleted FPS limit function in Application.
* Deleted gzip-hpp dependency.
* Tiny implementation of compression/decompression functions in c.
* Refractoring.
* Changed Make to CMake bassed build system.
* Deleted all Makefiles.
* Support for IDE (vs, ...), windows toolchains and UNIX systems (not tested).
* C/C++ definitions for Linux platform.
* Improved MC_API definition.
* Removed mc prefix from util functions.
* Moved MC_INTERNAL_BREAK_POINT macro to common.h.
* Created UNIX scripts for install dependencies and build MC.
* Fix Documentation/ files.
* Created lib directories (lib/ and include/lib/).

New in rd-132211-3 - 14-08-25:
